desc: DailyPac based in Brisbane is specialty food containers and bags supplier. We have stock various sizes of plastic container that handle heavy duty , microwave and freezer safe, takeaway food, fruit punnet, reusable and dish washable. For single use, wooden and paper boxes have stock. Compostable Biodegradable packaging

layout.text: for food service on the table and on the go. It has lid to suit for takeaway & delivery meal
